column2: SELECT sp.specobjid,sp.ra,sp.dec,sp.z,sp.class AS cls, sp.subclass AS subcls, sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u AS mag_u, sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g AS mag_g, sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r AS mag_r, sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i AS mag_i, sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z AS mag_z,  w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2, w.w3mpro AS w3, w.w4mpro AS w4 into mydb.MyTable from SpecPhoto AS sp  JOIN wise_xmatch AS xm ON sp.objid = xm.sdss_objid JOIN wise_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr WHERE   (sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r > # AND   sp.zwarning=#)    UPDATE mydb.MyTable SET      subcls = &&& WHERE    subcls == &&& OR subcls == &&& OR subcls == &&& SET      subcls = &&& WHERE   subcls == &&& SET      subcls = &&& WHERE   subcls == &&&
